Package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.managers

@NonNullByDefault package nl.pim16aap2.animatedarchitecture.core.managers
This package contains managers that manage different certain aspects of the plugin. These managers are responsible for managing various tasks such the structure specifications, the limits of the plugin, the delayed command inputs, the tool users, the hooks for animated blocks, the different types of structures, the database connections, the power blocks and the hook for animations.
